items.sentence: Tom didn't see the accident, and I didn't either.
That isn't the main reason Tom wanted to do that.
The doctor told my father to cut down on smoking.
I had a jack, a king and three queens in my hand.
I have no idea where we are or where we're going.
I can't remember the last time I had so much fun.
I take my clothes to the cleaner's twice a month.
I found the secret compartment quite by accident.
I require absolute loyalty from all my employees.
I always wanted to make an around the world trip.
